summary: A racemenu and CBBE body preset for one of my Skyrim characters
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3]Been thinking about giving her preset for a while, finally got around to doing it. Here it is.
-------------------------------------------
Just unzip and drop the Kelsii.jslot file into the racemenu "presets" folder located at [i]Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets[/i] (If there is no preset folder, simply create one)

Then just get into the game, open up the racemenu, presets and select her name.
As a bonus to anyone interested I will also upload the Bodyslide preset for Kelsii. To install the bodyslide preset, just put the Amodel.xml file into [i]Skyrim\Data\CalienteTools\Bodyslide\SliderPresets[/i]
--------------------------------------------
[b][u]To get the face exactly how I have them in the pics:[/u][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] version 3.4.5 or greater is required.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS Hairdos[/url] is required.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] is required. (I use the goosebump version)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url] is required

If you want the body to be the same as well:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url] latest version is required.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]Outfit Studio[/url] is also required.[/size]

[size=6][color=red]NOTE![/color]
[/size][size=3]The hair she uses is physics based and will require [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?]HDT[/url] and note again that if you use a TBBP or BBP you will also need to download the optional BBP fix in the KS Hair files otherwise your bouncy boobs will become crushed as the hair physics and boob physics interfere with each other.[/size] 

Outfits in the pictures are the...
HDT Shadow Cat Armour
and
HDT Bosmer Priestess Armor
and
Monno's Bikinis
The first two are no longer available on Skyrim Nexus, but I'm sure the internet has them somewhere.[/center]
author: ShannasLiva
